i|\u4e80\u4e95 \u548c\u7f8e|Kamei Kazumi}}, a 55-year-old woman\n*{{nihongo|Michihiro Kanda|\u795e\u7530 \u9053\u5f18|Kanda Michihiro}}, a 46-year-old man\n*{{nihongo|Kazu Kasai|\u6cb3\u897f \u548c|Kasai Kazu}}, a 58-year-old woman\n*{{nihongo|Yoshiko Miyasaka|\u5bae\u5742 \u826f\u5b50|Miyasaka Yoshiko}}, a 56-year-old woman\n*{{nihongo|Seij\u014d Miyazaki|\u5bae\u5d0e \u6210\u57ce|Miyazaki Seij\u014d}}, a 63-year-old man\n*{{nihongo|Katsumi Ogawa|\u5c0f\u5ddd \u514b\u7f8e|Ogawa Katsumi}}, a 42-year-old man\n*{{nihongo|Takako Taguchi|\u7530\u53e3 \u8cb4\u5b50|Taguchi Takako}}, a 29-year-old woman\n*{{nihongo|Tomoko Tanaka|\u7530\u4e2d \u667a\u5b50|Tanaka Tomoko}}, a 49-year-old woman\n*{{nihongo|Yoshiko Yoshino|\u5409\u91ce \u82b3\u5b50|Yoshino Yoshiko}}, a 45-year-old woman\n==Results==\n{{Komae city assembly election, 2007}}\n===Candidate results===\n{{Election box begin|title=2007 Komae city assembly election<ref name=g2>https://go2senkyo.com/local/senkyo/10064</ref>}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Independent (politics)|candidate=Takako Taguchi|votes=2207|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Liberal Democratic Party (Japan)|candidate=Shigemi Suda|votes=1585|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Japanese Communist Party|candidate=Etsuo Suzuki|votes=1433|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Komeito|candidate=Takashi Sasaki|votes=1386|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Independent (politics)|candidate=Kazu Kasai|votes=1374|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Liberal Democratic Party (Japan)|candidate=[[Yoshiyuki Kuriyama]]|votes=1351|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Komeito|candidate=Kazumi Kamei|votes=1343|percentage=|change=}}\n{{Election box winning candidate with party link|party=Komeito|